\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Lately the messages have been light and\'a0inspiring and that is cool\'85that is\'a0actually one of my goals\'a0because at my core I\'a0believe most\'a0people know what they shoudl do\'85they just lack the inspiration and motivation to do it. \'a0Today\'85is\'a0not one of those days\'85because there is too much at stake.
\f1 \
\ls1\ilvl0
\f2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 I asked myself this week what would I want someone to say to me if I were sitting\'a0where\'a0you were and there was so much at stake?\'a0
\f1 \
\ls1\ilvl0
\f2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 So today, I want you to be ready\'85I\'92m not talking to anyone in particular, I\'92m not mad, I\'92m actually in a great place\'a0right now and my hope and prayer is that you would join me by the end of the message
\f1 \
\ls1\ilvl0
\f2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Because the problem as I see it, as I\'92ve counseling with people, as I\'92ve seen people struggle is this\'85
\f1 \
